  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA32">
<l>pāṟkaṭalum vēṅkaṭamum pāmpum paṉivicumpu</l>
<l>nūṟkaṭalu nuṇṇūla tāmaraimēl – pāṟpaṭ</l>
<l>ṭiruntār maṉamu miṭamākak koṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>kuruntocitta kōpā lakaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The milk ocean, Vēṅkaṭam, the snake, the dewy sky,</l>
<l>the ocean of treatises and the heart of the one who sits arranged on the</l>
<l>lotus with fine fibres<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">The person (titled with an honorific in iruntār) to be sitting on the lotus might even be Śrī or Brahmā.</note>, [these] he took as [his] places,</l>
<l>the cowherd who broke the wild lime tree.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
